# model-viewer monorepo

London Dynamics fork of **model-viewer** — a web component library for interactive 3D models (glTF/GLB), published as `@london-dynamics/model-viewer`. npm workspaces with 5 packages under `packages/`.

## Node.js

Requires **Node.js 18** (see `.nvmrc`):

```
export NVM_DIR="$HOME/.nvm" && source "$NVM_DIR/nvm.sh"
```

## Key commands

See root `README.md` for full details.

- **Install**: `npm install`
- **Build**: `npm run build` (all workspaces)
- **Build (faster)**: `cd packages/model-viewer && npm run build:dev` — dev rollup when iterating on `model-viewer` only
- **Test**: `npm run test` or `npm run test:ci`
- **Serve**: `npm run serve` — port 8080; docs at `/packages/modelviewer.dev/`, editor at `/packages/space-opera/editor/`
- **Lint**: `npm run lint` (no-op; `.eslintignore` excludes all packages)

Feature, docs, and example conventions → [`.cursor/rules/README.md`](README.md)
